{"tid":1657014,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［抗爭完左？？？］點解冇人圍林奠 比佢咁安樂入立法會","createTime":"2019-10-16T01:19:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T11:13:39.000Z","uid":6181,"like":38,"dislike":80,"uniUserReply":72,"replies":[{"pid":"aadeba947e575352849006d9002163a21d125d1d","tid":1657014,"uid":6181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T01:19:52.000Z","msg":"往時《施政報告》要做足保密功夫，同事對報告嘅內容都要守口如瓶。今年考慮到情況特殊，各位局長喺我發表《施政報告》前可以率先公布惠民嘅新措施，已經講咗比市民聽嘅有：<br />\n<br />\n＋ 動用105億元幫助舊樓業主維修樓宇、電梯同埋加強消防設備；<br />\n<br />\n＋ 加強兒童體能智力測驗中心服務，同埋喺學校更好支援有自閉症嘅學生；<br />\n<br />\n＋ 喺天水圍天秀路公園旁邊嘅空地設立臨時街市，最快出年年尾完工啟用；<br />\n<br />\n＋ 為精英運動員提供更多資助，備戰明年東京奧運，增加各體育總會嘅資助培養年輕運動員，同埋支持體育學院建新大樓。<br />\n<br />\n我下個禮拜三發表嘅《施政報告》會公布更多措施，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">希望能夠順利入到立法會大樓啦。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n#民生無小事 #2019施政報告 #2019PolicyAddress #林鄭月娥 #CarrieLam"},{"pid":"bb8e9fced96c2613bfd1dea9c8a7e0f2f1a5a37f","tid":1657014,"uid":47605,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T01:20:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bHH8FUF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbHH8FUF.jpg&h=3fd66e79&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"4623d7e2a26aa3ad85d1abd1d18337a2bb3a7dab","tid":1657014,"uid":170812,"like":69,"dislike":0,"score":69,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T01:20:50.000Z","msg":"Who fucking care with the puppet?"},{"pid":"827d39c4ba07d57d30affdb686e8b6ddfcf85296","tid":1657014,"uid":6181,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T01:20:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8jTof.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8jTof.jpg&h=d703f2a1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"46665cc9a17736d5f37ea9145c32a512ea310ecc","tid":1657014,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T01:21:34.000Z","msg":"【香城施政報告2019】群策群力 轉危為機<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"http